Market Analysis and Insights

Energy and Nutrition Bars Market

Data Bridge Market Research analyses that the global energy and nutrition bars market to account USD 1.01 billion by 2028 growing at a CAGR of 3.70% in the forecast period of 2021-2028.

Energy bars are defined as the additional bars which contains both, cereals as well as high-energy food. The energy bars are helpful because they give an individual an adequate amount of nutrition and offer the fast energy. These bars help to meet the dietary gaps as they are strengthened with vitamins and minerals. Major companies are involved in the production of these bars that are fulfilled with the nutrition because of its advantage in the fast nutrition amongst individuals.

Growing demand for flavoured energy bar and clean label product are the major factors attributable to the growth of energy and nutrition bars market.Rising need for sports nutrition and consumer preference for health and wellness products are the driving factors influencing the growth of the energy and nutrition bars market.

Surge in the product innovation in nutrition bars and energy bars will boost the opportunities for the growth of energy and nutrition bars market.

On the other hand, availability of substitute products in the market and negative impact of product recalls as well as challenges related to the product distribution will restrict the growth of the energy and nutrition bars market. Lack of awareness about the new products in developing countries will challenge the market growth.

